title: Johnny's Gone Fishing
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, American, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A coffee-shop/cafe has vegan choices that are not labeled and may possibly be able to make other items vegan. Vegans please inquire. Serves locally-roasted fair trade coffee and espresso drinks, snacks, beverages, baked goods, paninis, wraps, farm fresh products and local artisan goods. Has live music.
